You have to be patient and wait. The devel build report is usually
available about 9:45 AM Seattle time. Changes need to be checked in by
5PM the previous evening in order to be included in the next day's
build.

Once you are happy with your changes, you need to bump the version
number of your package or it will not be propagated to our web
site/repository.

Thanks,
Dan


